premise_source_doc_sentence: Wasalu Muhammad Jaco  (  born February 16 , 1982  )  , better known by his stage name Lupe Fiasco  (  -LSB- ˈluːpeɪ -RSB-  )  , is an American rapper , record producer , and entrepreneur .
The song was written by Lupe Fiasco , and produced by producer Soundtrakk .

It was intended to be the first single of Everywhere , the first of three CDs of Lupe Fiasco 's triple album , Lupe Fiasco 's LupE.N.D. , but because of its release being withheld , there was speculation circulating that it may be the first single of his third album , Lasers .
`` Kick , Push '' is the first single released from Lupe Fiasco 's debut album , Lupe Fiasco 's Food & Liquor .
